snippet.title: LOST ORBIT: Terminal Velocity Release Announcement
snippet.description:
Launching July 16th on PlayStation®4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch and Steam (PC, Mac, Linux)

Prepare to once again embark on a perilous journey filled with deadly asteroids, orbital boosts and the emptiness of space, but this time escape space pirates and more in LOST ORBIT: Terminal Velocity, the definitive version of the fast-paced, dodge ‘em up game from PixelNAUTS Games.

Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/lost-orbit-terminal-velocity-switch/
Xbox: https://www.microsoft.com/en-ca/p/lost-orbit-terminal-velocity/c0fc4grrj2fc?rtc=1&activetab=pivot:overviewtab
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/372320/LOST_ORBIT_Terminal_Velocity/
PS4: https://store.playstation.com/en-ca/product/UP2185-CUSA01657_00-PNAUTSLOSTORBIT1?smcid=pdc%3Aus-en%3Aweb-pdc-games-lost-orbit-ps4%3Aleadproductinfo-buy-download%3Anull%3A
